data.description: This home is in a convenient location just minutes from the historic city of Fernandina Beach, the beautiful beaches of Amelia Island, Jacksonville International Airport, and Naval Stations Kings Bay and Mayport. Nestled in the sought-after Villages of Woodbridge neighborhood in a great school district, this home has been owned by the seller since its construction. With 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, a 2-car garage and fenced spacious backyard, this home is ideal for people and pets alike! This home's open kitchen, dining, and living space make an inviting atmosphere for entertaining family and friends. The owner's suite is located at the rear of the home and the split-bedroom floor plan provides extra privacy when hosting guests! The roof was replaced in 2022 and the A/C was replaced in 2021. NO CDD FEES!
